text: Daniela Melchior (born November 1, 1996) is a Portuguese actress. She is best known for playing Ratcatcher 2 in The Suicide Squad (2021). She also voiced Spider-Gwen in the Portuguese dub of Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse (2018). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese movie actors Category:Portuguese television actors Category:Portuguese voice actors Category:Models (profession)
